featured_reviews.review_id:
This masjid complex has two masjids and haveli of syedna Ismail Badruddin ra. The small masjid belongs to era of syedna Ismail Badruddin maula.
The haveli is a must see place. Made in wood and load bearing structure is simple, elegant and beautiful. The lintels of doors have text written on them which is hand written by Syedna Ismail Badruddin maula himself. His family lineage upto bharmals is also inscribed here. A memorabilia of fatimid history in India!!!
